{"tid":1090043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母終國人!! 中國旅客帶豬肉香腸入境 日本首次檢出非洲豬瘟活病毒","createTime":"2019-04-03T07:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T12:45:13.000Z","uid":80042,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"96830255796d6182c2c6ab1e6b5a1e5cc3973aa2","tid":1090043,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"日本農林水產省在昨日（2日）公佈日前於中國旅客所攜帶的2條豬肉香腸中檢出非洲豬瘟活病毒，是首次檢出具傳染性的活病毒入境個案。<br />\n<br />\n今年1月12日，兩名中國旅客經中部國際機場入境時被搜出2條豬肉香腸，經化驗後確實內含非洲豬瘟活病毒。估計兩名旅客乘坐由上海及青島出發的航班到日本，二人並無直接關係，豬肉香腸均為手信之用。 <br />\n<br />\n中國旅客帶豬肉香腸入境 日本首次檢出非洲豬瘟活病毒<br />\n之前在日本國內發現的均為非洲豬瘟的基因，未知傳染性如何，今次是首宗檢出具傳染性的活病毒個案。日本農林水產省為進一步加強防範外地傳入病毒，若旅客非法攜帶肉製品入境，將會記下護照號碼等資料並要求涉事旅客寫契約書承諾不再重犯。若重犯將報警並有機會作出起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/26925/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%B8%B6%E8%B1%AC%E8%82%89%E9%A6%99%E8%85%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E6%AA%A2%E5%87%BA%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%B1%AC%E7%98%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92/1/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link&amp;fbclid=IwAR3r838-c7NPyzLRXLsPIw7DZ2mU-gvUCipvVWHtKI7ypSRLItWt_Qh9N4E#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F26925%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E8%2582%2589%25E9%25A6%2599%25E8%2585%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E7%2598%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%2F1%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_content%3Dlink%26fbclid%3DIwAR3r838-c7NPyzLRXLsPIw7DZ2mU-gvUCipvVWHtKI7ypSRLItWt_Qh9N4E%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D2&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5BAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=6dad00ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/26925/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9